2000-10-06   Daiki Ueno  <ueno@unixuser.org>

	* elmo-vars.el (elmo-imap4-stream-type-alist): New variable.
	(elmo-pop3-stream-type-alist): New variable.
	(elmo-nntp-stream-type-alist): New variable.

